response.original_title: RIAT 2016 - The Royal International Air Tattoo
response.overview: Lockheed Martin's F-35B Lightning II performed its first ever international display at Air Tattoo. Other highlights of the 2-hour main feature include displays by the F-22 Raptor', a Polish MiG-29, the Turkish Air Force F-16 'Solo Turk' and the final display of the French Air Force 'Ramex Delta' Mirage 2000N duo.
